### GET account features – liability-side classification code (resolved at current wall-clock time)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/account-features/LIAB_INAS_2026_Q1Q2
X-Client-ID: {{clientId}}

### GET account features – resolved as at a specific point in time
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/account-features/LIAB_INAS_2026_Q1Q2?asAt=2026-01-15T12:00:00Z
X-Client-ID: {{clientId}}

### PUT account features – configure liability interest on a liability-side node
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/account-features/LIAB_INAS_2026_Q1Q2
X-Client-ID: {{clientId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$uuid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "effectiveDatetime": "2026-01-02T00:00:00Z",
  "features": {
    "liabilityInterest": {
      "enabled": true,
      "interestRate": 0.0250000
    }
  }
}

### PUT account features – configure asset interest on an asset-side node
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/account-features/ASST_BTRM_2026_Q1Q2
X-Client-ID: {{clientId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$uuid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "effectiveDatetime": "2026-01-02T00:00:00Z",
  "features": {
    "assetInterest": {
      "enabled": true,
      "interestRate": 0.0550000
    }
  }
}

### PUT account features – suppress an inherited property via explicit absence
# explicitAbsences terminates inheritance resolution for the named properties without
# providing a replacement value. The key is the feature name; the list contains the
# property names to suppress.
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/account-features/LIAB_INAS_2026_Q1Q2
X-Client-ID: {{clientId}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$uuid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "effectiveDatetime": "2026-01-02T00:00:00Z",
  "features": {},
  "explicitAbsences": {
    "liabilityInterest": ["interestRate"]
  }
}
